es==\n\n{{Empty section|date=April 2020}}\n\n==Results==\n\n{{Empty section|date=April 2020}}\n\n==Branches==\n\n==References==\n\n1. https://www.iitimpulse.com\n2. https://www.zaubacorp.com/company/IMPULSE-JEE-INSTITUTE-PRIVATE-LIMITED/U80904BR2016PTC032913\n3. https://m.sulekha.com/impulse-jee-institute-pvt-ltd-ballygunge-kolkata-contact-address\n4. https://m.indiamart.com/impulse-jee-institute-pvt-ltd/sitenavigation.html\n5. http://www.findglocal.com/IN/KOLKATA/1778903938994912/IMPULSE-JEE-INSTITUTE-PVT.-LTD.\n6. https://m.economictimes.com/company/impulse-jee-institute-private-limited-/U80904BR2016PTC032913\n7. http://www.massivedynamics.site/phe/\n8. https://www.lawyerservices.in/IMPULSE-JEE-INSTITUTE-PVT-LTD--U80904BR2016PTC032913--66421291\n\n{{Uncategorized|date=April 2020}}\n", "text_old": "<!-- Please do not remove or change this AfD message until the discussion has been closed. -->\n{{Article for deletion/dated|page=Impulse Jee|timestamp=20200411192919|year=2020|month=April|day=11|substed=yes}}\n<!-- Once discussion is closed, please place on talk page: {{Old AfD multi|page=Impulse Jee|date=11 April 2020|result='''keep'''}} -->\n<!-- End of AfD message, feel free to edit beyond this point -->\n{{Infobox organization\n| image = Impulse_Jee.png\n| alt = \n| caption = \n| map = \n| formation = \n| headquarters = 6/1/1E,Swin How Street,Anil Moitra Road(Opp to Durgabari) Near to Senior South point school,Kolkata-700019\n| coords = \n| services = [[Cram school]] for IIT-JEE and various engineering entrance examination\n| language = English,Hindi\n| leader_title = \n| leader_name = \n| leader_title2 = \n| leader_name2 = \n| leader_name3 = \n| leader_title3 = \n| leader_title4 = \n| leader_name4 = \n| key_people = Prakash Ranjan (Founder)\n| main_organ = \n| parent_organization = \n| subsidiaries = \n| budget = \n| name = \n| type = [[Cram school]]\n| image_border = \n| size = \n| msize = \n| malt = \n| mcaption = \n| map2 = \n| abbreviation = \n| location = \n| 